---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const effectiveDate = 'July 16, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Duddcash Studios collects, uses, and protects your information."
>
  <section class="legal">
    <div class="legal__inner">
      <h1 class="legal__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal__date">Effective date: {effectiveDate}</p>

      <p>
        Duddcash, LLC, doing business as Duddcash Studios ("we," "us"),
        operates duddcashstudios.com. This policy explains what information we
        collect when you use our site, how we use it, and the choices you
        have.
      </p>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <p><strong>Information you give us.</strong> When you submit our contact
      or application forms, we collect the details you provide — typically your
      name, email address, company or brand name, and any project information
      you share. We use this only to respond to your inquiry, evaluate your
      project, and communicate with you about our services.</p>
      <p><strong>Information collected automatically.</strong> Our hosting and
      video-delivery providers may automatically log standard technical data
      such as IP address, browser type, and pages requested for security and
      performance purposes. We do not run advertising trackers, and we do not
      sell personal information.</p>
      <p><strong>Local storage.</strong> The site uses your browser's local
      storage for functional purposes only — for example, remembering site
      layout preferences and whether you've dismissed an announcement. This
      data stays in your browser and is not used to track you across other
      sites.</p>

      <h2>How we use information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To respond to inquiries and applications you send us</li>
        <li>To provide, operate, and improve the website</li>
        <li>To protect against spam and abuse</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Service providers</h2>
      <p>We rely on a small number of vendors to run this site. They process
      data only as needed to provide their services to us:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Netlify</strong> — website hosting and form handling</li>
        <li><strong>Bunny.net</strong> — video streaming and content delivery</li>
        <li><strong>Google Workspace</strong> — storage of form submissions and email</li>
        <li><strong>Cal.com</strong> — call scheduling, if you book a call with us</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>We keep inquiry and application information for as long as needed to
      handle your request and for reasonable business record-keeping. You can
      ask us to delete your information at any time.</p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on where you live, you may have rights to access, correct,
      or delete personal information we hold about you, and to object to or
      restrict certain processing. To exercise any of these rights, email us at
      the address below and we will respond promptly.</p>

      <h2>Children</h2>
      <p>Our site and services are not directed to children under 13, and we
      do not knowingly collect personal information from them.</p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>If we make material changes, we will update this page and revise the
      effective date above.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions or requests:
        <a href="mailto:action@duddcashstudios.com">action@duddcashstudios.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  .legal {
    padding: 140px 3.9vw 100px;
    min-height: 70vh;
  }

  .legal__inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .legal__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .legal__date {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .legal__inner h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 36px 0 12px;
  }

  .legal__inner p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .legal__inner ul {
    margin: 0 0 14px 20px;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .legal__inner li {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    list-style: disc;
  }

  .legal__inner a {
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal {
      padding: 110px 20px 70px;
    }
  }
</style>
